price. =E2=80=9CI&#39;ll give you the rest December 31, but either way, you=
 keep the deposit,=E2=80=9D he told Gaston. He mortgaged his house, pulled =
together some other money he had around, and wired the deposit to Gaston.<b=
r/></td>
